- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with the proof of a conservative extension of Peano Arithmetic. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the least likely category, but cannot be completely ruled out as the paper employs a computational semantics.
